Data Fields:¶

  • Date: record date
  • Country/Region:
  • Province/State: contains NULL
  • Lat: Lattitude
  • Long: Longitude
  • Confirmed: Number of confirmed cases
  • Recover: Number of recovered cases
  • Deaths: Number of deaths
